Project Change State
====================
This module allows the user to change the status of multiple projects
simultaneously.


Usage
=====

>From the Project Tree View select the projects you want to change the state
for and go to action > Change Project Status


.. image:: https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas
